#   gperf        >= 3.0
#   GNU make     >= 3.81 
# 
# Run dependencies:
#   libevent     >= 1.3 (older versions may work)
#   libpcre      >= 7.6
#   Berkeley DB  >= 4.5
# 
# Test suite dependencies:
#   CUnit        >= 2.1
